   <p begin="00:23:50.721" end="00:23:51.931" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピッピッピッ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:23:52.098" end="00:23:54.934" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピカチュ…　ピ～カ～！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:23:55.059" end="00:23:55.893" style="s1"><span style="s2">（階下に落ちる音）</span></p> 
